value.0: Vibroweapons are a family of weapons that utilize high-speed sonic vibrations to turn a regular object into a deadly weapon; most commonly found on swords, vibrogenerators can also be found on axes, pikes, knives, etc. Almost anything with a blade has the potential to be turned into a vibroweapon.
